name: Bluedio A (Air) Stylish Wireless Bluetooth Headphones with Mic (Black)
short_description:
Product Description

Color: Black

Compatibility 
The Bluetooth perfectly works with your smartphone, tablet or Bluetooth enabled MP3 player. 

Instruction tips 
Turning 3D sound on: when the headphones are playing music via Bluetooth, press the MF Button and Vol Button together then release the buttons immediately. You will hear an indication note, the 3D sound is on. 

Specifications 
Bluetooth version: V4.1 
Supported Profiles: A2DP, AVRCP, HSP, HFP 
Bluetooth operating range : up to 10m (free space) 
Transducers: 57mm×2 
Impedance: 16 
Frequency response: 15Hz-25KHz 
Sound pressure level (SPL): 118dB 
Bluetooth music/talk time: up to 20 hours 
Standby time: up to 1000 hours (about 41 days) 
Charging time: 2.5 hours for full charge 

In the box 
Bluedio A Bluetooth headphones 
User manual 
Carry case with a buckle 
Audio cable; Talk cable with remote(only for talk not for music); Y audio cable 
USB charging cable 
Pouch for cables

name: Universal 360 Rotating Magnetic Car Air Vent Mount Mobile Phone Holder Stand for smartphone
short_description:
A universal mounting solution that will hold most smartphones as well as their cases from 2-4 inches wide
* Magnetic mount securely holds your device with no adhesive residue
* Small and compact Size with a sophisticated design to provide a fully functional cradle-less mounting solution
* Designed for safe driving, won\'t block your sight
* Spring loaded one click lock and release feature to provide a strong clamped hold to users vent blade while also minimizing vibrations to your device
* Comes with 2 metal plates to go with different phone size
* Position in any direction, provides 360° viewing angles
* Easy installation. Simply attach the magnetic plate to your smartphone, mount with one hand and go

*Please note: The magnet may cause some interference to compass function. It will return back to normal after removing the phone from the mount.
 

Specification:


Material: Plastic and rubber
Weight: 50g
dimensions: 8 x 6 x 4.5 cm
Color: silver

name: Blue color Bluedio N2 Sports Wireless Bluetooth Stereo Earbuds Headset
short_description:
With Bluetooth 4.1 A2DP Wireless Stereo Headset Sport
Earphone headphone. The advanced Bluetooth 4.0 technology(8 times the
bandwidth compare over the Bluetooth 2.1 standard). Which can can work
well with iPhone 5s/5c/5/4s/4/3/2; iPad series/iPod/ iTouch; Samsung
Galaxy S4/S3/S2/Note2/Note3/Galaxy/Nokia/HTC/aTT/Toshiaba/Sony all Smart
phone and All Tablet/PC/Laptop.


With the best Audio Performance
Stereo -
Bluetooth 4.1 - Wireless 30 feet distance - Sport - In the ear.
Lightweight, comfortable earbuds - quality sound on the go. Media on the
move. Subway commute, Coffee shop lounging, Taking a walk, Whatever
your scenery, enjoy it more while listening to your own tunes - all
without the hassle of connecting with a wire.


Cutting-edge sound
Featuring the
state-of-the-art Bluetooth 4.1 standard (8 times the bandwidth over the
2.1 standard) , these earbuds produce clear, full sound. The
snug-fitting ear tips block out peripheral noise letting you enjoy your
media - free of distractions. Simply take control.


We put the most used functions (adjust volume, skip tracks, power,
and phone functions) in easy reach and even included a power meter on
IOS 5 and over. With up to 5 hours of play time between charges, don't
worry about charging often, but when you do, the clip-on charger does
the job with ease. Sportier audio.


Bluetooth sporting headset
Allows clear
communication; Enables use as a headset. Music and phone controls ensure
ease of use, digital noise cancellation technology


Product Features:


Sweat and moisture-proof
Effectively prevent sweat and rain interfere with headset operation. Make every drop of sweat dancing with music.


Reproduced true sound
Crafted with 10mm dynamic
driver, and CCAW voice coil created surprising full-bodied timbre,
clear and bright, better transient response, restore true sound of your
favorite singer.


6th generation CVC noise reduction

Significantly improves receive path voice signal by sophisticated
algorithm technology and altering the spectral shape of the receive path
signal


YES or NO
Voice command say Yes or NO decide
whether to pick a call, free your hands to do what you want. If you are
busying, say Yes to pick a call,say No to reject a call.


  • Voice prompts
  • EQ, Multi-point
  • Call waiting, 180hrs standby, Real stereo
  • Last call redial, Noise reduction
  • Voice control

name: Fitmate U8 Smart Watch Silicone Band For Android & iOS,Black - Fitmate U8
short_description:
The Fitmate U8 Bluetooth Smart Wrist Watch lets you stay in step with the time and the world in a new age way. This smart wrist watch features a high resolution, 1.48inch, capacitive touch display that enables you to see what matters at a glance. A high quality, black, plastic strap augments the watch’s matching black, stainless steel case further. The Fitmate U8 smart watch pairs with tablets, smartphones, and PCs that operate on Android v2.3 or higher. It is also compatible with IOS operating systems via its Bluetooth v2.0. It enables hands free calls and gives you instant and discreet access to your mobile’s phonebook, notifications, and more. Those who have paired their Android smart devices with this accessory will also get notifications when they receive messages on WeChat, Twitter, Facebook, Skype, WhatsApp, and other such apps. Android users can also click pictures remotely with this Fitmate U8 smart watch. An onboard pedometer accurately counts the number of steps you take throughout the day. The timepiece incorporates an altitude meter, stopwatch, and barometer for your convenience
  • Hands Free Phone Call
  • Remote Control Phone Music & Camera
  • SMS,Whats App,FB,WeChat etc notification
  • Alarm,Calendar,Calculator,etc
  • Pedometer,Barometer & Sleep Monitor

short_description:
Main Feature
Main Features:
Iconic powerful bass resonance of Bluedio: 57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, with the iconic Bluedio surging low-frequency shock, let you feel the bass resonate deep in the chest, enjoying the best sound quality. Clear and transparent bass, mids and treble, fully exposed to all the details of song, you can hear what the artists really want you to hear, Coldplay or Linkin Park concert played in your ear
Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1: With robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, comes with ultra-long using of 40 hours music, 45 hours talk and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time, the same battery, decrease up to 40% power consumption compare to Bluetooth 4.0. Comfortable wearing: Custom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs, artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture, ensure long lasting comfort in various rugged circumstances
Convenience: Just a plug with audio cable, then listen to your favorite tracks without using any battery, no matter how long is your playlist. H-turbine also incorporate 4 languages voice prompt(Chinese, English, French, Spanish), to communicate with you in your language

name: Wireless Bluetooth Headset Handsfree Earphone Mic For iPhone 6 6 6S Plus Samsung S7 Note 5 (Golden)
short_description:
Product Features




Color: Golden

Size (LWH): 1.02 inches, 0.65 inches, 0.59 inches
  • Minimum Rated Talk Time: 3 hours
  • Minimum Rated Standby Time: 120 hours
  • Battery Type: Lithium Ion

Tips:

1. Pairing :If you can't pair the Bluetooth with

your phone , please make sure this headset has been going into pairing

mode. (Turn the Bluetooth on and keep press the function key until the

LED light flashing Red and Blue).

2.Connecting: If your phone

can't search the bluetooth, please kindly try to restart your phone. If

you can't pair it, please feel free to contact us. We will try our best

to help you.

3. Quantity : This mini earbud is just one earbud for your right or left ear. Not a pair.



4. Size : The size of this Bluetooth is derived from the test date of

our engineers. It can be suitable most person's ear. Please kindly

understand it could be not suitable for you completely. We will be much

appreciate if you would like to contact us when you find the earphone is

not fit for you.

5.Language Change : If you change the language by accident, please try to according to the below step to change it back :
1). Power it off.
2). Power it on and let go of the button before it tries to pair.
3). Now the blue light is on (but not in pairing mode).
4). Hold the button again for a second. The mode will then change back to English.

Package Include:
1. 1x earbud
2. 1x instructions
3. 1x USB charging cable

name: Bluedio UFO Bluetooth Wireless Headphone with Microphone , Purple , UFO
short_description:
The Bluedio UFO Bluetooth 3D Sound Headset provides excellent sound with great bass and a good battery life. It offers an incredible playback time of 25 hours thanks to the Bluetooth 4.1 low power technology. The Bluedio UFO headset employs a unique 8 driver design that reproduces every single note with absolute clarity. Correspondingly, the Bluedio innovative PPS8 technology lets you experience a more balanced and crisp audio. The headset is compatible with tablets, smartphones or Bluetooth enabled MP3 players. It is fantastically crafted with superior quality Al Ti alloy for enhanced durability.


Product Top Features:

• Frequency: 5Hz -25000Hz
• Bluetooth 4.1
• Weight: 335g


Get The Beats Going

The Bluedio UFO reviews are a testimony to this headset's outstanding audio experience. Delivering a deep, powerful, and balanced sound is the exclusive PPS8 technology with the new innovative 8 driver design. The headset supports Bluetooth 4.1 technology that saves power and offers a whopping 25 hour music time. Plus, it also lets you use this device wirelessly within a 30ft range. Dramatically enhancing your music experience is the 3D Sound effect function that brings all of your music to life and offers an immersive experience.


Top Notch Looks

The Bluedio UFO specs comprise of a combination of features that make this headset a favorite. It is constructed using Al Ti alloy material that features high durability and reliability. Plus, its lightweight design eliminates ear fatigue brought on by prolonged listening.

short_description: The black colored Bluedio Turbine Hurricane HT Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones are one of a kind. They were made to please demanding users looking for a wireless headset with great audio technologies. The HT Headphones comes with several high tech features found in today’s high end headsets, and are without a doubt one of the best wireless, high tech headsets. They diminish the need for cables and make listening to songs a clutter free experience. With regards to the audio performance, the HT headset is quite magnificent. Its technology is based on 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers that deliver a well balanced sound, with clear bass, and incredible treble, which together allow you to listen to the tiniest details of a song. The noise cancelation and noise reduction features efficiently reduce ambient noise while talking or listening to music. As far as convenience is concerned, the headset features custom fit, supra aural, soft earmuffs made of artificial protein leather to ensure long lasting comfort. The language prompt on the HT headset comes ready with 4 languages, English, Spanish, French, and English, to make communicating easy.

Clear and transparent bass, mids and highs, fully exposed to all the details of the song, you can hear what the artists really want you to hear, Coldplay or Linkin Park concerts are simply playing around your ear.2- Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1: With robust high-speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, comes with ultra-long 40 hours music, 45 hours talk and 1625 hours (around 67 days) standby time, the same battery, decrease up to 40% power consumption compare to Bluetooth 4.0. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction effectively reduce ambient noise while talking, make far-end listener cannot hear what you said become history, just like talking face to face.3- Customized function: Audio Sharing allows you to connect to another H(Shooting Brake) headphone via audio cable, share music feast with your friends instantly(*recommended to use headphones with an impedance of 32 or higher). Seamless connect two Bluetooth devices simultaneously, listen to music or enjoy foreign blockbusters, do as you think about it.4- Comfortable wearing: Custom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs, artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture, ensure long lasting comfort in various rugged circumstances.5- Convenience: Just a plug with an audio cable(*buy separately), then listen to your favorite tracks without using any battery, no matter how long is your playlist. name: Smart Watch Rubber Band For Android,Red - U8
short_description: The U8 Bluetooth Smart Wrist Watch lets you stay in step with the time and the world in a new age way. This smart wrist watch features a high resolution, 1.48inch, capacitive touch display that enables you to see what matters at a glance. A high quality, white, plastic strap augments the watch’s matching white, stainless steel case further. The U8 smartwatch pairs with tablets, smartphones, and PCs that operate on Android v2.3 or higher. It is also compatible with iOS operating systems via its Bluetooth v2.0. It enables handsfree calls and gives you instant and discreet access to your mobile’s phonebook, notifications, and more. Those who have paired their Android smart devices with this accessory will also get notifications when they receive messages on WeChat, Twitter, Facebook, Skype, WhatsApp, and other such apps. Android users can also click pictures remotely with this smartwatch. An onboard passometer accurately counts the number of steps you take throughout the day. The timepiece incorporates an altitude meter, stopwatch, and barometer for your convenience.

name: Bluedio Active Noise Cancelling Over-ear Wireless , Black , F800
short_description:
Features:

ANC technology- F800 adopts the Active Noise Cancelling technology, which continuously measures, compares and reacts to outside noise—then cancels them with the opposite signal, to bring you crystal-clear sound.
F800 uses a bass boost system to better coordinate the noise cancelling function. After the ANC is activated,the bass will automatically boost while retaining the original sound of music.
F800 is built with high-quality stainless steel, which greatly enhances its durability and makes it strong enough to survive life. Besides, the hollow headband design makes it quite lightweight.
F800 utilizes the 57mm ultra big driver to deliver full range sound in new perfection. It allows you to hear clear and rich details as well as a powerful bass.
The headband of F800 is covered bysoft synthetic protein leather, and the ear cushions are padded with memory foam rich in protein. All these will provide an amazing comfort for all-day listening.
Color: Black
Model Number: F800

name: Bluedio Vinyl Over-ear Wireless Bluetooth Headphones , Blue
short_description:
Bluetooth 4.1- With lower power consumption, the latest Bluetooth 4.1 chip can ensure a long-lasting battery life. Besides, it’s easily compatible with Apple devices like iPhone, and iPad as well as Android tablets and smartphones.
Rotational structure- Vinyl has been designed to be rotational. The horizontal rotation helps to save more space, which makes it convenient for you to carry. The vertical rotation allows you to listen with just one ear.
Exquisite craft- Vinyl is built with an Al-Ti alloy body, which is strong and lightweight. Every radian is carefully considered to build the comfortable streamline. The adjustable band can be accurately set to fit different head forms.
3D sound- The built-in 3D sound can effectively strengthen the sound field to make the sound more stereo. Simply turn on it, you will hear sound from all directions as if you are on the scene.
Comfortable- The artificial leather earmuffs are padded with memory foam which is rich in protein, so it can stay over your ears comfortably for a long time.

name: Bluedio T4 Over-ear Wireless Bluetooth Headphones , Red
short_description:
ANC Technology: T4's Active Noise Cancelling technology cuts off surround noise significantly and lets you enjoy your music in its pure form. The ANC technology works in tandem with the 57mm drivers, so you can enjoy the immersive experience of listening a top notch music sound stage. You can always count on T4 headphones for crisp,vivid highs.
Vibrant Bass/Treble and crispy Mids: T4's unique Cavity Design minimizes interference from other frequencies around you, enhances the bass response. The ear cup design includes specially designed vents, which not only adjust airflow and ventilation, but also contribute to a full-bodied, vibrant and bouncy bass.
Durability: In accordance with Bluedio's no-compromise on quality approach, the headphone is built with premium materials and high quality Polymers with chrome finish. All hinges, frames and sliders reflect high quality build. T4 is a durable headphone that will last for years.
TYPE-C Three in One Interface: Turbine 4th generation uses TYPE-C three in one interface which supports charging and data transmitting. It can be plugged in both sides, so it’s very easy to use.

name: Bluedio F2 Over-ear Wireless Bluetooth Headphones , Black
short_description:
Bluedio Vector Flow Technology: Faith 2 has a unique design wherein a ventilated back chamber in each ear cup of the headphone can propel air out and equalize air pressure on both sides of the headphone ear cans. This results in enhanced bass reproduction and an unparalleled sound fidelity.
ANC technology: Faith 2 adopts an advanced Active Noise Cancelling technology algorithm, which continuously measures surrounding white noise, compares and reacts it by canceling it with the opposite frequency signal, to bring you crystal-clear sound with exceptional noise canceling.
Oval over-ear design: Faith 2 comes with state of design with premium materials and oval ear cups that nicely sit around your ears. The result is a great looking headphones with exceptional comfort. You can wear the headphones for hours and not worry about any fatigue.
New design, new colors: The design of Faith 2 headphones are created to sync with your tastes and makes a hip fashion statement about your style. These are most elegant headphones in the product category, that comes in two colors and has a rotatable design.
Bluetooth 4.2: Faith2 is equipped with latest Bluetooth version 4.2, that makes these future proof in technology. You get maximum battery life due to low power consumption, which means you can leave your charger back when you head to long journeys with your Bluedio Faith 2 headphones.

name: Bluedio Air Fashion Bluetooth Headset 3D Sound - Black
short_description:
Listen to all your music with unbeatable depth and crystal clarity on the Bluedio Air Fashion 3D Sound Bluetooth Headset. This headset focuses on providing a well balanced sound, longer battery life, and heavenly comfort. As per the Bluedio Air specs, this stylish wireless headset is easy to connect with Android or iOS devices alike and has high definition speakers with clear, powerful sound. The headset incorporates HD Diaphragm technology that lets you hear the difference even in your favorite tunes. Turn the 3D sound on for when you want to experience a fuller and dynamic experience. Besides, these Bluedio Air headphones adopt the power efficient Bluetooth v4.1 technology that lets you go wireless and listen to songs for up to 20 hours. Adding to this greatness is the Bluedio Air wireless headset’s construction. It has a twistable headband, together with pivoting earcups and soft padding to create a comfortable fit.

Physical Features

Key Features

15 Hz-25 KHz

Bluetooth V4.1

music/talk time up to 20 hours

Talk On the Go

The Bluedio Air reviews found online will fortify your resolve when it comes to making a decision about purchasing a sturdy headset. Equipped with an intelligent control audio cable and mic, this headset lets you enjoy handsfree communication. Its built in mic makes sure your voice is transferred clearly to the other end. Plus, since this headset is Bluetooth compatible, you can be free of wires and its tangling issues.

Enhance Your Style Quotient

The Bluedio Air headphones are styled with sleek curves, oval earcups, and vivid patterns. It sports a white finish with colorful geometric figures strewn across its entirety; these accentuate its look. In addition, the headphone’s space saving design makes it easier to store when not in use.

name: Bluedio Air Fashion Bluetooth Headset - White
short_description:
Sporting a stylish look, foldable headband, soft ear pads, and a Bluetooth 4.1 chip, the Bluedio Air Fashion Bluetooth Headset is here to deliver big sound! This headset is a combination of performance, style, and convenience. It has an ergonomic design, soft PU leather cover, and comfy ear pillows that offer utmost comfort for prolonged listening. In addition to the high quality music, this Bluedio Bluetooth headset also lets you answer calls hands free while on the go via its Intelligent Control Audio cable. It also enables you to pause and play music with the click of a button. The Bluedio Air Fashion Bluetooth Headset sports a stylish white color with colorful geometric figures. With a long runtime of 1100 hours, the Bluedio headset reviews are bound to be favorable.

Key Features

Bluetooth

Frequency response: 15Hz~25KHz

Micro USB

Sensitivity: 110dB

Superior Sound

This wireless headset by Bluedio is built in with a 24bit HD chip that helps deliver real Hi Fi surround sound. You get a deep bass, high range, and natural vocals, which together provide the ultimate audio experience. The headset comes with a 57mm driver unit that delivers high end audio output.

Comfort First

The Bluetooth Music Headset is sturdy enough to handle your rigorous lifestyle without wilting. Its headband is made out of high toughness PC material with soft PU Leather cover. It's highly flexible and can also be folded. This on ear headset has soft memory sponge fillings that ensure complete comfort during prolonged listing hours. This, in turn, facilitates a comfortable and customized fit.

Button Remote and Mic

Sporting a stylish look, foldable headband, soft ear pads, and a Bluetooth 4.1 chip, the Bluedio Air Fashion Bluetooth Headset is here to deliver big sound! This headset is a combination of performance, style, and convenience. It has an ergonomic design, soft PU leather cover, and comfy ear pillows that offer utmost comfort for prolonged listening. In addition to the high quality music, this Bluedio Bluetooth headset also lets you answer calls hands free while on the go via its Intelligent Control Audio cable. It also enables you to pause and play music with the click of a button. The Bluedio Air Fashion Bluetooth Headset sports a stylish white color with colorful geometric figures. With a long runtime of 1100 hours, the Bluedio headset reviews are bound to be favorable.

Key Features

Bluetooth

Frequency response: 15Hz~25KHz

Micro USB

Sensitivity: 110dB

Superior Sound

This wireless headset by Bluedio is built in with a 24bit HD chip that helps deliver real Hi Fi surround sound. You get a deep bass, high range, and natural vocals, which together provide the ultimate audio experience. The headset comes with a 57mm driver unit that delivers high end audio output.

Comfort First

The Bluetooth Music Headset is sturdy enough to handle your rigorous lifestyle without wilting. Its headband is made out of high toughness PC material with soft PU Leather cover. It's highly flexible and can also be folded. This on ear headset has soft memory sponge fillings that ensure complete comfort during prolonged listing hours. This, in turn, facilitates a comfortable and customized fit.

name: U-Watch Smart Bluetooth Watch Black (BW01-BLK)
short_description:
The U Watch BW01 BLK Smart Bluetooth Watch is a stylish looking smart watch that is compatible with a broad range of smart devices. The timepiece’s 1.44inch, touch enabled display has a maximum resolution of 128 x 128 pixels, providing you with crisp, clear detail that makes reading off it easy. Besides showing the current time, you can also access your smartphone’s call records, messages, camera, alarm, stopwatch, and music player fluidly, with this smartwatch that has a preinstalled Nucleus operating system. The accessory can also be used to locate your smart device, set call reminders, and calculate the number of calories you have burned while engaging in any physical activity. Also featured on this digital timepiece is a barometer, pedometer, and a thermometer. A novel feature of this smartwatch is its integrated 0.7W speaker that produces brisk audio. U Watch smart watch reviews also praise its Bluetooth connectivity, which quickly establishes a reliable connection with your smart device. You can save all your data, as well as up to 1500 contacts in the device's Phonebook, thanks to the inclusion of the internal 32MB NOR flash storage.

Provides Easy Access to Your Smartphone’s Features

Pairing the U Watch Bluetooth smartwatch for Android and iOS devices with your smartphone lets you access your mobile’s features without even touching the device. The timepiece can be used to access your smartphone’s call records, messages, camera, alarm, stopwatch, and music player with a mere touch on the accessory’s 1.44inch, touch enabled display.

Perfect Companion

The Smart Watch Bluetooth smartwatch can help you locate your smart device and even set up call reminders. The accessory also features a pedometer that can precisely track the number of calories you have burned through the day.

name: Bluedio H (Turbine) Bass Stereo Wireless Bluetooth 4.1 Headphone Headset
short_description:
Features:
Iconic powerful bass resonance of Bluedio:
Unexpected 57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, with iconic Bluedio surging low-frequency shock, let you feel the bass resonate deep in the chest, enjoying the best sound quality. Clear and transparent bass, mids and highs, fully exposed to all the details of song, you can hear what the artists you really want to hear, Coldplay or Linkin Park concerts are simply playing around your ear.
Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1:
With robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, comes with ultra-long 40 hours music, 45 hours talk and 1625 hours (around 67 days) standby time, the same battery, decrease up to 40% power consumption compare to Bluetooth 4.0. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction effectively reduce ambient noise while talking, make far-end listener cannot hear what you said become history, just like talking face to face.
Customized function:
Audio Sharing allows you to connect to another H headphone via audio cable, share music feast with your friends instantly(*recommended to use headphones with
impedance of 32 or higher). Seamless connect two Bluetooth devices simultaneously, listen to music or enjoy foreign blockbusters, do as you think about it.
Comfortable wearing:
Custom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs, artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture, ensure long lasting comfort in various rugged circumstances.
Convenience:
Just a plug with audio cable(*buy separately), then listen to your favorite tracks without using any battery, no matter how long is your playlist. H-turbine also incorporate 4 languages voice prompt(Chinese, English, French, Spanish), to communicate with you in your language.
Ongoing luxurious Bluetooth 4.1 Headphone, delighting the world.

Luxurious music enjoyment is always unreachable. For this reason, Bluedio keep hard working on 3 years of R&D and testing, manage to customize a wireless headphone with unrivaled timbre, adapted to a variety of rugged circumstances and highly cost- effective. Thoughtful design, unexpected superior sound, make luxury become reasonable, this is Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 headphone. Thus, H is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows, merely 40ms audio latency breakthrough defects of sound and picture are not synchronized while watching movie via Bluetooth. It also work as a BT receiver connecting mobile phone and professional amplifier wirelessly. Insert Micro-SD card which saved with music files into the headphone SD card slot. Remove Micro-SD card under Micro-SD card mode, headset will change to FM mode. Insert Micro-SD card under FM mode, headset will change to Micro-SD card mode. But it may affect function of the headset,
do not suggest the above usage.

1. Elegant round dial solves that
aesthetic issue



2. Advanced MTK2502C chip, Bluetooth 4.0
technology

240 x 240 full view display and smooth touch experience

of your daily activities and calculates the calorie burned



5. Sleep monitor records your sleep
patterns and analyzes your sleeping quality



6. Sedentary reminder helps you promote a
healthy lifestyle



7. Professional grade heart rate sensor,
with dual modes: healthy heart rate and sports heart rate modes



8. Sync calls, call logs, contracts,
messages and notifications from paired phone via Bluetooth



9. Find phone function lets you easily
locate the lost phone



10. Support remote control over cellphone
camera



11. Support remote control over music
play on the phone



12. The screen automatically wakes and
lights up when wrist is raised



13. 5 groups of alarm clocks can be set,
with ringtone and vibration alert types

Siri support, stopwatch and more

change

to wear during rigorous workouts or outdoor activities

1. Model: K88H



2. Processor: MTK2502C



3. Bluetooth Version: 4.0

9. Waterproof: Yes

7.0 and Above

Italian, Polish, Portuguese, Russian, Spanish

0.47)" / (4.4 x 4.4 x 1.2)cm (L x W x H)

Main Functions:



1. Bluetooth Function



With Bluetooth V4.0, this smart watch is
available for smart phones with Bluetooth function.



2. Sync Function



a. Sync phonebook with Smartphone;



b. Sync SMS with Android and ios phones;
iphone cannot use messaging menu.



c. Sync incoming call with Smartphone;



d. Sync music with Smartphone.



3. Smart Watch Design



a. Prefect Design: Full HD IPS Screen,
1.22 inch screen



b. With 2 wallpaper and 3 theme, more
convenient for daily operation



4. Siri Function



Talk to the watch, your phone will do
what you said : check weather, call to, send message to(this function is only
for iPhone)



5. Looking Phone



When you can't find your phone, our smart
watch will be useful! As long as you use the "looking phone" function.
(for iPhone, when you use this function, you should open the Fundo Wear app
first)



6. Remote Capture



You can take photos of whole family
without other help, just use "remote capture" function. (for iPhone,
when you use this function, you should open the phone camera first)



7. Remote Notify



When software on Android and iOS phone
has some information, the smart watch will remind you. So you will never miss
them even if in noisy party!(Install Fundo Wear 
on cell phones first)



8. Various Time Show



Different moods use different time
displays.



9. Pedometer



This smart watch can record steps,
calories and distance. Let you know your sports data, adjust your exercise
program and get a healthier life!



10. Sleep Monitor



When you sleep, it will monitor your
sleep. Let you know your sleep quality right away.



11. Sedentary Reminder



Take a rest to avoid fatigue! Our smart
watch has sedentary reminder function to keep fit! You can choose the reminder
time.



12. Heart Rate Monitoring



Monitor your heart rate, help you do
reasonable exercise!



13. Standard Time and Military Time



Standard Time and Military can suit
different people.



14. Anti-lost

name: plantronics M70 Bluetooth Headset
short_description:
The Plantronics M70 Bluetooth® headset is so lightweight and comfortable you may forget you’re wearing it. During set up, you simply follow the voice prompts to select English, Spanish, or French for the audible status alerts on talk time, battery
level, connection, and more. You can also control music tracks and volume without touching your smartphone.
If you forget it in the car or at the office, the M70 knows to enter its DeepSleep® hibernation mode to conserve the battery. Using the M70 is so easy that you can finally free your
cheek from your smartphone.

specifications
  • Talk Time: Up to 11 hours*
  • Standby Time: Up to 16 days*
  • DeepSleep Standby Mode: Up to 180 days*

  • Multipoint Technology: Pair and maintain connections with two phones and
  • answer calls from either phone

  • phones and networks

name: Plantronics ML2 Bluetooth Headset
short_description:
Simple and easy to use with the Plantronics ML2 Bluetooth headset. Free your hands from your phone. 

Made for

New users looking for reliable sound that make hands-free calling as easy as possible 

Main Benefits:

Reduces noise and echo

Pairs with two phones

Fits either ear comfortably

Optional earloop

Voice dialing* (*Smartphone dependent)

ml2 product show

Easy Set-up and Clear Calls

ML2 enables people to make hands free calls whether multitasking on or off the road. It has a compact product design and Plantronics’ hallmark all day comfort. The headset can be worn with or without the optional earloop and the comfortable eartip can be worn on either ear. It also offers multipoint, redial, voice dialing through the phones voice engine, call answer/end/reject.

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Wireless Bluetooth 4.1 Stereo Headphone Headset white color
short_description:
After extensive research, Bluedio has found that current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such as serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons, after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset.
Iconic powerful bass resonance
57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound quality.
Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1
With the robust 72 MHTz and 16/32 bits high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while speaking.
The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows.
Customized function
Audio Sharing allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and listen to music as you please!
Convenience
Just plug in with an audio cable, you can listen to your favorite music tracks. 
(Headset button function only used for bluetooth connection, cable connection button function is invalid)

The Hurricane H also has voice prompts in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Chinese).
Comfort
Custom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.
Specification:
Drivers: 57mm speaker X 2
Transducer type: Dynamic
Bluetooth version: V4.1

name: Bluedio T 3 Bluetooth Stereo Headphones,3D sound ,SD card slot
short_description:
Zn alloy body to ensure quality and texture
T3 Plus is beautifully crafted with excellent Zn alloy material which features high performance. The exquisitely built Zn alloy frame and body ensures it sturdy enough to be unbreakable and durable. 

57mm titanizing diaphragm for quick response
T3 Plus adopts the all titanizing 57mm diaphragm to enhance the resolution, lower the THD(Total Harmonic Distortion) and make the sound more dynamic, swift and fierce, which ensures you hear even the slightest details and enjoy every wonderful moment.

Totally new 3D sound effect
T3 Plus is the first headphones of Turbine Series to adopt 3D sound effect, which means you will have a totally lively and stirring experience. Simply turn on the 3D sound to immerse yourself in the stereo surround sound effect and to let your ears enjoy the stirring rock concert.

Micro SD card playback
T3 Plus supports Micro SD card slot extension (maximum 32GB). Just insert a Micro SD card loaded with your favorite songs, no need of mobile phones or other auxiliary devices, you can directly enjoy music. Besides, you can transfer files through the USB connector anytime and anywhere, which means you no longer have to repeat one song at wonderful moments.

Memory foam earmuffs to ensure long-wearing comfort
The ear cups of T3 Plus are padded with memory foam which is rich in protein. It is very soft and ventilated. All we want to do is to bring you comfort, to protect your ears and give you a new feeling of wearing.

Line-in and line-out playback
T3 Plus supports input with the 3.5mm audio cable, you can still enjoy your favorite music even if the battery runs out. It can also connect to other headphones so that you can share your favorite music with your friends.

Foldable design, more convenient and portable
We specially strengthen the telescopic arm to ensure that it can bear over 5 thousand times stretching and bending. The foldable design makes it very convenient and portable.

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Over the Ear Headset - Silver
short_description:
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 wireless stereo headset has been created after extensive research. Bluedio has found that current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such as serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons, after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H headset.

Iconic Powerful Bass Resonance

57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and bluedio's iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound quality.

Ultra-Long Operation And Carefree Calling From Bluetooth 4.1

With the robust high speed cpu of bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the bluedio turbine hurricane h boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while speaking.

Customized Function

Audio sharing allows you to connect to another h headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and listen to music as you please!

Comfort

Custom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.

Convenience

Just plug in with an audio cable (sold separately), and listen to your favorite music tracks. The hurricane h also has voice prompts in 4 languages (english, french, spanish, and chinese).

Product Details

  • Brand: Bluedio
  • Model: Turbine Hurricane H
  • Color: Silver
  • Type: Over the Ear
  • Drivers: 57mm speaker X 2
  • Transducer type: dynamic
  • Bluetooth version: V4.1
  • Frequency range: 2.4GHz-2.48GHz
  • Operating distance: up to 10m (free space)
  • Bluetooth profiles: A2DPAVRCPHSPHFP
  • Impedance: 16
  • Frequency response: 20Hz-20kHz
  • Sensitivity: 110dB
  • Distortion:<0.1%(THD)
  • Music playtime: up to 40 hours
  • Talk time: up to 45 hours
  • Standby time: up to 1625 hours
  • Charging time: about 2 hours
  • Operational temperature: -10 to 50°C

name: Best Smart Watch U8 Plus White Color
short_description: The U8 Bluetooth Smart Wrist Watch lets you stay in step with the time and the world in a new age way. This smart wrist watch features a high resolution, 1.48inch, capacitive touch display that enables you to see what matters at a glance. A high quality, white, plastic strap augments the watch’s matching white, stainless steel case further. The U8 smartwatch pairs with tablets, smartphones, and PCs that operate on Android v2.3 or higher. It is also compatible with iOS operating systems via its Bluetooth v2.0. It enables handsfree calls and gives you instant and discreet access to your mobile’s phonebook, notifications, and more. Those who have paired their Android smart devices with this accessory will also get notifications when they receive messages on WeChat, Twitter, Facebook, Skype, WhatsApp, and other such apps. Android users can also click pictures remotely with this smartwatch. An onboard passometer accurately counts the number of steps you take throughout the day. The timepiece incorporates an altitude meter, stopwatch, and barometer for your convenience.

name: Bluedio Extra Bass Wireless Bluetooth Headset , PPS12 Drivers , Black , UFO Plus
short_description:
Features and Specifications:


• PPS12 technology, the combination of three drivers especially for trembles and another three drivers for mids and bass, makes sure that you will enjoy all range of frequency to the fullest extent. You can expect crisp, vivid highs from this headphone.
• Cavity Design gives isolation from some ambient sounds, enhances the bass response and pushes the airflow of both front and back cavity to achieve resonance. The cavities, along with specially designed vents, which adjust the ventilation, contribute to a full-bodied, vibrant and bouncy bass reproduction.
• To protect your ears, Bluedio U Plus adopts over-ear earmuffs and stereo clipping craft. It not only brings you natural and comfortable wearing, but also reduce leaking voice.
• The ear cups is designed to be rotated backward for 180 degrees, mainly considering the special requirements of DJ.It also works when you want to stay aware about what`s happening around you.
• Built with premium materials, Al-Ti alloy. It owns sturdy, lightweight alloyed frames, yokes and sliders.
• Bluetooth version: 4.1
• Bluetooth operating range: up to 10 meters
• Bluetooth music/talk time: about 25 hours
• Standby time: about 1000 hours
• Charging time: about 2.5 hours
• Headphones weight: 397g

name: Bluedio Vinyl Plus Luxury Elegant Classic Wireless Bluetooth Headphones , Black , VPB
short_description:
Vinyl plus, whose design inspiration comes from the classic and retro vinyl record, is another classic headphones created by Bluedio team. The flexible and streamline appearance design is just like the vinyl CD. It adopts the ultra-big 70mm driver to produce the most natural and original sound and won't let you miss any sound detail. Unique and distinctive, vinyl plus aims to build the highest listening standard and bring you a wonderful experience with high quality sound.


Product Features:

• Round ear cups and twisted headphone arms, which resembles needle of an old record player, give the headphone an unique, blingbling , classic and elegant looking
• With ultra-big 70mm drivers, the headphone is capable of producing more details.
• Has tight bass, warm smooth midrange and high frequencies
• The 3D mode works as an amplifier to enhance the sound effects, especially for the bass.
• Activating 3D sound will reproduce a richer sound with depth and thickness
• Artificial leather earmuffs padded with memory foam which is rich in protein. It is very soft and ventilated. Not only protect your ears, but also guarantees comfortable wearing. Screen printing process to make it look textured; slide shaft with accurate degree (up to 32mm) to satisfy different head forms and to reduce leaking voice

 

Product Specifications:

• Bluetooth version: 4.1
• Bluetooth profiles: A2DP, AVRCP, HSP, HFP
• Bluetooth transmission frequency: 2.4GHz to 2.48GHz
• Bluetooth operating range: up to 33 feet (free space)
• Frequency response: 15hz-25,000Hz
• Bluetooth music/talk time: about 20 hours
• Standby time: up to 1100 hours
• Charging time: 2 hours for full charge
